	<h1 class="title">久石让为这款游戏制作音乐，会增加你的期待值吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/495481/small/495481.jpg?1456747733" alt="">
